title: Little Thieves
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2qqHNiP

by ohwise1ne

“If you come out now, Omega, I’ll make this easy for you.”

His voice carries clearly through the house, and it’s almost as sinful as the smell of him, suffocating her as she shrinks back against the wall of his closet.

“Or maybe… you don’t want this to be easy.” A pause. “Yes. Oh, yes. I can smell it on you, little girl. You can’t hide from me.”

Rey breaks into the wrong house. Kylo Ren catches her in the act.

summary:
New headcanons for clones this time and
its not sad… well entirely sad. As a child Moddy had growing pains so
bad it kept her...
body:
New headcanons for clones this time and its not sad… well entirely sad.

As a child Moddy had growing pains so bad it kept her from sleeping and made her cry and gave her stretchmarks everywhere, even on the back of her knees.

Because of that I started thinking, I didn’t become an adult in ten or less years so logic dictates that the clones would have rather large stretchmarks generally all over as I highly doubt the Kamino’s would dedicate resources to stopping the harmless stretchmarks from becoming a thing since I highly doubt Jango did not have some of his own.

Ergo, clones with stretchmarks along their sides, back of their knees, along their legs, in their armpits and along their arms.

tags: am i still salty yes i am
tlj wasted a lot of time floating out there with woobie kylo ren possibilities
but it undeniably did its see it from a mile away subversion at the end
to show that kylo ren is a garbage man responsible for his own misery
bc he made his own choices all along
and rey shut it down and cut him out
to the point where i really dont care to see her fight him again
but id pay to see her kick his ass and send him to jail i guess :)
summary: i feel so sad for everyone who’s deluded themselves into thinking kylo ren is the Only Possible Person from whom rey can find...
body:
i feel so sad for everyone who’s deluded themselves into thinking kylo ren is the Only Possible Person from whom rey can find unconditional love and acceptance

when in tlj he literally laid out the condition of “you’re garbage only i can understand you, but you have to stand back while my new army murders your only other friends and destroys the galaxy” then tries to kill her when she refuses

my sadness wears off the second i start thinking about how this viewpoint conveniently always erases finn (who actually loves and supports rey unconditionally but go off i guess)
